WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.709 --> 00:00:07.210
Hi, I'm style expert Alison Deyette and this
is the Playtex Bra Makeover Series.

00:00:07.210 --> 00:00:12.800
We selected ten real women with real bra problems
and flew them to New York for a professional

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:13.940
bra fitting.

00:00:13.940 --> 00:00:19.050
We helped each discover the perfect bra for
her shape and lifestyle.

00:00:19.050 --> 00:00:23.230
Meet Christine.

00:00:23.230 --> 00:00:27.789
My name is Christine, I am 45 from New York
and am an administrator.

00:00:27.789 --> 00:00:32.970
I had a thyroidectomy, I had cancer and it
was tough but I am back!

00:00:32.970 --> 00:00:37.630
Her recent thyroid surgery has her feeling
better than ever about herself.

00:00:37.630 --> 00:00:42.899
Let's see if Playtex can help Christine continue
the self-improvement by finding her the perfect

00:00:42.899 --> 00:00:43.929
bra.

00:00:43.929 --> 00:00:49.190
I have never been fitted for a bra before,
name a problem and I have had it.

00:00:49.190 --> 00:00:59.249
Straps slipping off, falling out of my sides,
the underwire that poke out of your shirt!

00:00:59.249 --> 00:01:02.969
Christine I cannot avoid your bra problem.

00:01:02.969 --> 00:01:05.470
This bra is way too big on you!

00:01:05.470 --> 00:01:12.320
You have lost forty pounds and cannot read
the label!

00:01:12.320 --> 00:01:17.450
I know that you also don't like the under
wires but tell me why and any other issues.

00:01:17.450 --> 00:01:22.710
Well it pokes me, it sticks out like an antennae
through the t-shirt.

00:01:22.710 --> 00:01:26.340
Well we are going to banish the underwire!

00:01:26.340 --> 00:01:33.570
This bra is a 44 double D but I am going to
give you a bra makeover and I also have a

00:01:33.570 --> 00:01:37.689
surprise for you about this beautiful style.

00:01:37.689 --> 00:01:39.770
Let's go!

00:01:39.770 --> 00:01:44.829
To feel pretty and to stand up straight and
to have the girls look fabulous.

00:01:44.829 --> 00:01:48.359
It's an undergarment but it's about how you
see yourself and how you feel about yourself.

00:01:48.359 --> 00:01:53.640
I want to be a rocking hot grandma.

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:59.840
Alright, show me your brand new bra.

00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:03.570
It is the same bra but dramatically different!

00:02:03.570 --> 00:02:11.030
You were wearing a 44 double D but now you
are a 44 D!

00:02:11.030 --> 00:02:16.470
This is the 18 hour Comfort Lace detail throughout.

00:02:16.470 --> 00:02:28.250
It also has the airform fabric that is lining
all the way from the front to the back and

00:02:28.250 --> 00:02:29.530
it's actually pretty!

00:02:29.530 --> 00:02:33.320
Let's say the bra makeover is complete and
we have found you a perfect fit!

00:02:33.320 --> 00:02:36.470
They are standing up and saying hello!

00:02:36.470 --> 00:02:41.610
I look better and feel better, I feel fantastic.

00:02:41.610 --> 00:02:43.550
Thanks for the bra makeover Playtex!

